{"tid":2516553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[石頭 腳 戰狼又贏] 歐盟已暫停批准中歐全面投資協定？！","createTime":"2021-05-04T17:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T17:18:24.000Z","uid":108201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a432eaeeaa900a18b8b95104aee6ffc3f92efbcb","tid":2516553,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">外交部發言人</span></span></strong>聽日一定<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">用&rdquo;石頭 腳&rdquo;作文</span></span></strong>回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐盟高級貿易官員周二(4日)表示，鑑於中歐雙方在互相制裁之後外交關係惡化，歐盟已暫停批准中歐全面投資協定。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟轄下專責經濟政策的執行副主席東布羅夫斯基斯(Valdis Dombrovskis)周二接受法新社訪問稱，歐盟委員會<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">已暫停與中歐全面投資協定相關的政治接觸行動</span></span></strong>。"},{"pid":"a57a069e9dd26dcdc8cf5fcd0f90f9aa034b030b","tid":2516553,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"幾時又制裁歐盟官員同燒Nike <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"8a27bad20587e5cc1f746b63e1ff67b26d005f14","tid":2516553,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會又捉幾個德國人做報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"24210d4c4fdc1e181a2388e200e0bd04f60af6c3","tid":2516553,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"戰狼出動未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}